                    of <persName ref="http://syriaca.org/person/113">Jacob of Edessa</persName>, apparently in a different hand, addressed to one <quote xml:lang="syr"><persName>ܩܘܪܝܣܘܢܐ</persName><supplied xml:lang="en" reason="translation" resp="http://syriaca.org/documentation/editors.xml#wwright">(<foreign xml:lang="grc">Κύριος</foreign>, with the diminutive
